MENU_PKG_UDEV
  Here you will find config options for the udev packages.

SDECFG_PKG_UDEV_DEVDIR
  Per default udev does use /dev for the devices files. If you only want to
  test udev or use s.th. else on /dev you might like to adapt this setting
  accordingly (e.g. to /udev).
